Interface ByteValue

All Superinterfaces:
Comparable<ByteValue>, Mirror, PrimitiveValue, Value
public interface ByteValue extends PrimitiveValue, Comparable<ByteValue>
Provides access to a primitive byte value in the target VM.
Since:
1.3
